          "fromEmail": "notificaions@lockated.com",
          "toEmail": "={{$json.opportunity_owner_email}}\n",
          "subject": "=New Opportunity Assigned – {{$json.opportunity_title}}\n",
          "html": "=Dear {{$json.RecipientName}},\n\nA new opportunity has been created and assigned to you for evaluation and action.\n\nOpportunity Details:\n• Title: {{$json.opportunity_title}}\n• Description: {{$json.description}}\n• Status: {{$json.opportunity_status}}\n• Created On: {{$json.opportunity_created_at}}\n\nPlease review and initiate next steps.\n\nRegards,\nOpportunity Management Offic\n",
